# Origin of the API (scheme + host, NO path). Both clients use it: better-auth
# appends `/api/auth/*`, the REST client appends `/api`. So set the bare origin,
# e.g. https://api.colloidos.com — NOT https://api.colloidos.com/api.
#
# Leave empty for local dev: requests fall back to the SPA origin and the Vite
# proxy forwards /api -> :4000.
#
# Production (split subdomains, e.g. app.colloidos.com + api.colloidos.com):
# set the API origin here AND set COOKIE_DOMAIN=.colloidos.com on the backend so
# the better-auth session cookie is shared across the subdomains (first-party to
# both). See docs/features/auth-and-sessions.md.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
